name: Honor Of The Jedi
Lore: 'The final act of Luke''s ascension to Jedi Knighthood was sending off his father, draped in the garb of Vader.',
Text: 'Deploy on table. Unless opponent occupies three battlegrounds, each time you must lose Force (except from your card, battle damage or a Force drain at a battleground), reduce the loss by 2. (Immune to Alter while you occupy any battleground).',
